                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "content":  "### â‘¢b LIVE MODE\n\nReal pulls in parallel: Todoist (today+overdue), Google Calendar (today), Gmail (priority unread).\n\n**Needs credentials:** Google Calendar OAuth must be created in n8n UI before this branch runs.",
