                  {
                      "parameters":  {
                                         "method":  "POST",
                                         "url":  "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages",
                                         "authentication":  "genericCredentialType",
                                         "genericAuthType":  "httpHeaderAuth",
                                         "sendHeaders":  true,
                                         "headerParameters":  {
                                                                  "parameters":  [
                                                                                     {
                                                                                         "name":  "anthropic-version",
                                                                                         "value":  "2023-06-01"
                                                                                     },
                                                                                     {
                                                                                         "name":  "content-type",
                                                                                         "value":  "application/json"
                                                                                     }
                                                                                 ]
                                                              },
                                         "sendBody":  true,
                                         "contentType":  "json",
                                         "specifyBody":  "json",
                                         "jsonBody":  "={{ JSON.stringify({\n  model: $json.config.ai.model,\n  max_tokens: $json.config.ai.max_tokens,\n  messages: [\n    {\n      role: \"user\",\n      content: `You are the chief of staff for ${$json.config.persona.owner_first_name} at ${$json.config.persona.business_name}.\\n\\nWrite a morning briefing from this data. RULES:\\n- Lead with the single most important thing to act on today.\\n- Plain English. No jargon.\\n- Every item must have a clear action.\\n- Call out anything unusual (stale high-value deals, after-hours leads, missed follow-ups).\\n- Concise â€” 60 seconds to read.\\n- Bullet points, not paragraphs.\\n- End with \\\"Top 3 priorities today:\\\" as a numbered list.\\n\\nOutput in this exact markdown structure:\\n\\n**Morning Briefing â€” ${$json.date_label}**\\n\\n**Overnight:** \u003cone-liner about new leads / priority emails\u003e\\n\\n**Pipeline:** \u003cone-liner about deals + any stale callouts\u003e\\n\\n**Overdue:** \u003cbulleted list of missed follow-ups, or \\\"None â€” clean board\\\"\u003e\\n\\n**Today:** \u003cbulleted list of calendar events with times\u003e\\n\\n**Top 3 priorities today:**\\n1. \u003cpriority\u003e\\n2. \u003cpriority\u003e\\n3. \u003cpriority\u003e\\n\\nDATA:\\n${JSON.stringify({ overdue: $json.overdue_tasks, today: $json.today_tasks, calendar: $json.calendar_events, emails: $json.priority_emails, pipeline: $json.pipeline }, null, 2)}`\n    }\n  ]\n}) }}",
                                         "options":  {
                                                         "timeout":  30000
                                                     }
                                     },
